description:
VIVIENDAWEB SELLS EXTERIOR APARTMENT (living room and 2 bedrooms) on the 1st floor + 1 COVERED GARAGE SPACE (in the building on the 1st basement level) + 4-5 meter STORAGE ROOM in the building; approximately 121 m2 built according to deed; OUTDOOR POOL, PARKING SPACE, GREEN AREAS, outdoor summer POOL (June to September), PADEL COURT, GYM with equipment, and SAUNA;

LAYOUT: 2 DOUBLE BEDROOMS, both EXTERIOR (master bedroom + en-suite bathroom with window and walk-in closet), exterior LIVING-DINING ROOM, spacious fully equipped KITCHEN with all appliances; 2 BATHROOMS (master en-suite);

QUALITIES: Private gated community with summer POOL (June-Sep), PADEL COURT, GYM (with equipment), GARDEN, GREEN AREA, 24-HOUR/365-DAY SECURITY and concierge service; smooth paint, hot/cold air conditioning, reinforced door, climalit windows, laminate flooring, marble bathrooms, video intercom, 24-hour concierge, fitted wardrobes in hall, corridor, and bedrooms (walk-in closet in master bedroom);

EXPENSES: IBI (Property Tax) 964.14 euros/year, garbage fee 233 euros/year; community of owners (approx. 121 - built m2) - sold free of encumbrances, no mortgage, no tenants; immediate availability;

ENVIRONMENT AND LOCATION: apartment in the heart of the Chamberí district, very close to Ríos Rosas and José Abascal streets; METRO (Alonso Cano 3 minutes away and Ríos Rosas 4 minutes away); BUS (LINES 5, 12, 45); proximity to the renovated Santander Park (multi-sport facilities, gardens, fountains, running circuits), proximity to Teatros del Canal (theater, concerts, dance, and musicals); proximity to supermarkets (Ahorramas, Dia, Carrefour), neighborhood shops, restaurants, and banks; apartment in the heart of Chamberí, 10 minutes from Paseo de la Castellana; proximity to Modesto Lafuente health center and Clínica la Milagrosa;

PRICE: 1,100, 000 EUROS (apartment + 1 covered space in building + 1 storage room included); VIVIENDAWEB sells without commission or fees to the buyer; immediate availability; ideal for families or couples or for investors in a gated community in the heart of Chamberí. Ideal as an investment for long-term rental at 2,500 - 2,600 euros/month;

CONTACT: VIVIENDAWEB - Tel.
